Go to the Request Assistance point (Ticketing page)
Attempt to make a Ticket under any subject.
Requests you to log in;
PROCEDES TO SEND A CONFIRMATION EMAIL TO AN ACCOUNT THAT HAS BEEN ACTIVE SINCE SEASON FIVE.
ATTEMPTS TO LOG IN. SENDS MORE CONFIRMATION EMAILS TO SAID ACCOUNT. WHAT THE FUCK, RIOT PLEASE.
{{sticker:slayer-jinx-unamused}} {{sticker:zombie-brand-clap}} {{sticker:zombie-nunu-bummed}} 

Original Ticket - Gifting Skins:
Is it possible that you guys can allow certain skins to be unlocked during the holidays, or skins (mainly Ultimate and Legendary) that exist already, that still fall under official sales times, to be set on a timer where it is gifted on a particular day? (IE: Someone buys Elementist Lux say, today, and sets it to be usable after Christmas. Smart shit, yes?)

Again, this was FORCED by a GLITCHY TICKETING SYSTEM. RIOT CHECK YOUR SHIT, IT BE BROKEN SOMEHOWS.
